doctype html
html
  head
    meta(name="viewport",content="width=device-width")
    meta(http-equiv="Content-Type",content="text/html; charset=UTF-8")
    title Support Bernie Sanders
    style
      include invite.css
  body

    table(class="body-wrap")
      tr
        td
        td(class="container",bgcolor="#FFFFFF")
          // Content
          div(class="content")
            table
              tr(class="logo")
                td
                  img(height="120",src="http://bernbank.com/img/logoisolated2-email.png",alt="BernBank.com")
              tr
                td
                  p Hey everyone,
                  p Time again to fulfill the pledge you made to BernBank.
                  p Regardless of whether ​Bernie Sanders becomes the Democratic Party’s nominee, this is not about Bernie Sanders. 
                  p This is about progressivism. This is about ​<b>changing the world for the better.</b>
                  p That’s what your money is going to.
                  p We encourage you to follow through on your pledge and <b>continue to fuel the flame that Bernie has ignited.</b>
                  p Last week we had a total of #{totalCallers} callers who made more than #{threshold} calls. Since you pledged #{pledgeAmount} cent(s) per caller, your total pledge amount is $#{donationAmount}.
                  p
                    a(href="https://secure.actblue.com/contribute/page/bernbank?amount=" + donationAmount) <i>Click here to go to ActBlue and continue to empower the revolution.</i>
                  p Since we started, we have collected <b>$6458.99</b> for the campaign.                 
                  p The revolution is well under way. Millions of people are ready to change politics and bring back democracy. 
                  p ​<b>It does <i>not</i>​ end here.</b>
                  p - The BernBank Team
    // Footer
    table(class="footer-wrap")
      tr
        td
        td(class="container")
          // Content
          div(class="content")
            table
              tr
                td(align="center")
                  p(class="unsubscribe")
                    | Don't like these annoying emails? 
                    a(href="http://bernbank.com/actions/unsubscribe/" + email) Unsubscribe
        td
